{"tid":513281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網上熱話】麥當勞特選要求收窄，脆香雞翼不可要求「全翼」、「全膇」","createTime":"2017-12-29T10:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T10:54:01.000Z","uid":35221,"like":19,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"ef86a4c9126b46ace67ff9b1869d2862843c569c","tid":513281,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"【網上熱話】麥當勞特選要求收窄　脆香雞翼不可要求「全翼」、「全膇」 (18:38)<br />\n港聞<br />\n2017年12月29日 星期五<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171229/s00001/5273eae2fc6d23fadc8b6a6fc71e5731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171229%2Fs00001%2F5273eae2fc6d23fadc8b6a6fc71e5731.jpg&h=71ccc560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之1 - （明報資料圖片/明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171229/s00001/4d6778c5d43dd2f8b7dee0776a5822fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171229%2Fs00001%2F4d6778c5d43dd2f8b7dee0776a5822fb.jpg&h=32cbd036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之2 - (FB圖片)<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳麥當勞一份通告，指由本周三（27日）開始，顧客可特別要求的選擇收窄，以往包類的材料可選「加多」或「減少」，例如多菜或少酸瓜，但現在只可選擇「要」或「不要」；顧客現時再也不可選脆香雞翼要「全翼」或「全膇」；雪糕新地只可選「要」或「不要」花生或其他配料，而再不可揀選「加多」或「減少」。包類和新地的醬汁則可選「多醬」、「少醬」或「走醬」。<br />\n<br />\n通告指，新的處理方法是因要「簡化產品製作流程及步驟」。不少網民對麥當勞的決定感到驚訝，指尚可理解不能加多配料，但對於不能「減少」，有網民直言：「減少都唔得？」亦有網民留言表示，現在才知道原來點餐可以有特別的要求。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞回覆《明報》查詢，指公司不時「檢視並優化」食品製作流程和營運方式，但仍會「盡量配合」部分顧客對食品製作的個別要求，如走酸瓜、薯條走鹽、飲品少冰等，以切合不同顧客的喜好和需要，公司會繼續聆聽顧客意見，適時作出調整。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171229/s00001/1514535383721?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171229%2Fs00001%2F1514535383721%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=daa91a13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171229%2Fs00001%2F1514535383721%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=95a5fa21\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171229/s00001/1514535383721?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"8b544a554c147088bb5e101729c810844a8958e8","tid":513281,"uid":8830,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"麥當勞叔叔：罷食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31301161b02658a460b5a02d9ea2cab224ce0811","tid":513281,"uid":22675,"like":262,"dislike":10,"score":252,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"唔可以全翼真係影響最大"},{"pid":"4c0bcababdfac731aad54534a4bd79a1f5ecb402","tid":513281,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"都仲有機會係假，希望唔係真啦"},{"pid":"f5acc25df5ba7f190dcd6041108b18014681163c","tid":513281,"uid":9286,"like":72,"dislike":17,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"未食過全翼全膇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de9eebbe6ece332a3821f9f038ffe59a7d40c24","tid":513281,"uid":85819,"like":35,"dislike":60,"score":-25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74e56470528b586d7200c0d7f171a4d1ee32b9b5","tid":513281,"uid":18241,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"8de9eebbe6ece332a3821f9f038ffe59a7d40c24","tid":513281,"uid":85819,"like":35,"dislike":60,"score":-25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"新晉垃圾五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c552a218841cc629ab3af512cbf0fe7a9cf434cd","tid":513281,"uid":34223,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4c0bcababdfac731aad54534a4bd79a1f5ecb402","tid":513281,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"cit